{
  "uuid": "72826c5e30539a303f5f9ec3bce895e1",
  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Primary School Mathematics Teacher",
  "description": "<p><strong>About Us </strong></p><p>Founded by 2 expert young teachers, Math Vigilante is a tuition centre providing tutoring services for Math. We provide regular small group classes and 1-to-1 classes for students in primary, secondary and junior college levels. </p><p><strong>Who We Look For  </strong></p><p>We are looking for individuals who are passionate and committed to help students improve and cultivate their interest in teaching. Individuals who are proactive and takes initiative to inspire and nurture students to reach their academic potential.  </p><p>We have positions for teachers who are able to teach PSLE Math, or any levels between Primary 1 to Primary 6.  </p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities  </strong></p><ul><li><p>Plan, prepare, and deliver lessons. </p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Create a positive classroom culture by nurturing positive relationships with students.  </p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Drive improvement and outstanding performance for students. </p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Assess, record and report on development and progress of students. </p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Provide regular updates to parents on students’ performance and progress. </p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Ability to create social media deliverables, instagram/tiktok will be a bonus </p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements  </strong></p><ul><li><p>Post O-level graduate with good math academic records. </p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Preferably with some teaching experiences.  </p></li></ul><ul><li><p>A good understanding of the MOE syllabus. </p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Personable and able to work with young children  </p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Good communication and interpersonal skills.  </p></li></ul><p><strong>How to Apply </strong></p><p>Please note that to apply for this role, you must be residing in Singapore. </p><p>Do send an email to <a href=\"mailto:mathvigilante@gmail.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">mathvigilante@gmail.com</a> and chanyuxin13@gmail.com with the following documents for us to process your application.  </p><ul><li><p>Personal Resume  </p></li></ul><ul><li><p>‘O’ Level Certificate </p></li></ul><ul><li><p>‘A’ Level Certificate / Diploma Certificate and Transcript </p></li></ul><ul><li><p>University Degree Certificate and Transcript (if applicable)  </p></li></ul>",
